WEBVTT

00:00:01.699 --> 00:00:04.781
TAPE NUMBER SIX, MR ISAAC DANIELS.

00:00:05.108 --> 00:00:08.612
ir hot mir dertseylt ir hot gehat epes a kholem in tfise.

00:00:08.888 --> 00:00:10.569
vos iz geven der kholem?

00:00:11.419 --> 00:00:17.150
s'hot zikh mir gekholemt mayn tokhter kumt, un zi hot mir gebrengt esn.

00:00:17.697 --> 00:00:21.520
un zi zogt tsu mir, "tate hob nisht keyn moyre.

00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:28.676
in fertstn MAY, in dem akht un fertsikstn yor, vestu bafrayt vern."

00:00:29.847 --> 00:00:36.112
ikh hob zikh gegebn a khap oyf fun shlof. di akht un fertsikstn yor, ver vet oyshaltn azoy lang?

00:00:36.112 --> 00:00:38.412
ikh ken nisht arayn ikh ken nisht arumgeyn oyf di fis.

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:49.939
FINALLY, ikh bin dortn gevezn, vi ikh hob gezogt, ze'mir geven zibn un nayntsik mentshn in di ROOM.

00:00:50.265 --> 00:00:52.638
der vaser hot zikh gegosn fun di vent.

00:00:52.830 --> 00:00:59.085
m'hot dray mol in tog gemuzt shepn di vaser, vayl di kerpers hobn hot gevaremt dos ayz fun di vent.

00:00:59.496 --> 00:01:02.223
un un m'hot gemuzt shepn dos vaser oys.

00:01:04.035 --> 00:01:09.581
undz un di mentshn hobn gekrign, ir veyst vos heyst ferzhbe?

00:01:10.735 --> 00:01:16.921
blotern tsvishn di finger. un dos iz azoy ITCHY. geferlekh.

00:01:17.670 --> 00:01:20.803
hot men arayngerufn dem dokter, un s'a froy iz geven a dokter.

00:01:20.809 --> 00:01:25.393
un zi hot gekukt oyf di me- zi hot ge- zi hot zi hot gekukt bay yedn eynem azoy o,

00:01:25.787 --> 00:01:28.363
un got hot geholfn ale hobn gehat nor nisht ikh.

00:01:30.175 --> 00:01:34.961
zogt zi tsu mir, az du vest zayn der eltster, do,

00:01:35.018 --> 00:01:39.604
un du vest tsunemen dos broyt vos m'git arayn, vestu funander teyln,

00:01:39.604 --> 00:01:45.356
azoy az keyner zol nisht onrirn vayl s'zeyer zeyer onshtekndik.

00:01:46.678 --> 00:01:49.625
azoy iz gevorn az ikh bin gevorn der eltster in kamer.

00:01:52.264 --> 00:02:04.914
iz in in JUNE, JULY, un august, dos zenen geven di ergste monatn fun esn.

00:02:07.333 --> 00:02:13.489
dos vaser iz gevezn fun di bletlekh bletlekh fun fun burikes, ir veyst burikes.

00:02:13.489 --> 00:02:16.760
iz es grin, dos vaser iz es geven.

00:02:17.593 --> 00:02:24.742
oder s'geven a bletl s'arum geshvumen a shtikl bletl fun kroyt. un di resht iz vaser.

00:02:25.457 --> 00:02:32.285
az m'hot es gegebn in a hiltsern fas, gebrengt tsu firn arayn tsu tseteyln di zupn,

00:02:32.427 --> 00:02:37.061
hot zikh ongetsoygn fun der varemkeyt, m'hot es azh gefilt zikh.

00:02:37.590 --> 00:02:41.938
ikh hob di monatn keyn zup in gantsn nisht gegesn.

00:02:41.607 --> 00:02:43.140
vos hot ir gegesn?

00:02:42.248 --> 00:02:46.764
ikh hob gekrign in der fir fir hundert un fuftsik gram broyt.

00:02:47.631 --> 00:02:51.725
un m'hot arayngegebn a kesl mit gekokhte vaser.

00:02:51.917 --> 00:02:54.391
hob ikh gehat a tepl gekokhte vaser,

00:02:54.432 --> 00:02:58.543
mit dem shtikl broyt, un dos iz geven THAT'S IT. dos iz geven der tog esn.

00:02:58.212 --> 00:02:59.910
ir hot gearbet dortn?

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:07.436
NO. keyn shum geshlosener vos er iz in tfise, biz er iz nisht gemishpet, ken er nisht geyn oyf keyn arbet.

00:03:07.459 --> 00:03:09.869
ikh hob zikh gebetn, ikh hob gevolt geyn far arbet.

00:03:09.869 --> 00:03:12.566
un m'hot mir nisht gebe- tor nisht nemen oyf keyn arbet.

00:03:13.652 --> 00:03:16.953
vos ikh hob yo getun, ikh hob tsunoyfgenumen di vesh

00:03:17.196 --> 00:03:20.548
fun di mentshn un getrogn dortn vu m'vasht zey.

00:03:22.883 --> 00:03:30.667
SO azoy vi ikh bin, ikh hob dos nisht gegesn, iz in der tsayt funem krig,

00:03:30.667 --> 00:03:35.887
di mener zenen geven in di krig, zenen froyen geven zelner vos zey hobn gehitn di tfises.

00:03:37.328 --> 00:03:42.454
hot eyn froy hot arayngekukt, s'dortn geven a kleyn fentsterl arayntsukukn.

00:03:42.454 --> 00:03:47.733
hot zi gezen az ale esn di zupn, un ikh es nisht.

00:03:48.297 --> 00:03:51.733
ikh fleg may- ikh hob genumen nor ikh hob alts avekgegibn.

00:03:53.730 --> 00:04:03.528
SO ikh hob nisht gevust az zi observirt mikh. mit a mol kumt zi tsu,

00:04:03.585 --> 00:04:10.379
az m'lozt dikh arayn in kamer arayn, krigst aza groyse shisl mit a hiltsern lefl.

00:04:12.276 --> 00:04:17.382
efnt zi oyf di tir un ruft mikh tsu, gib mir dayn shisl.

00:04:18.385 --> 00:04:21.990
un zi brengt tsu a ful shisl azoy vi VEGETABLE,

00:04:22.857 --> 00:04:25.348
dortn iz alts geven farshidene VEGETABLES.

00:04:25.354 --> 00:04:30.376
a fule shisl! hob ikh tsugerufn nokh etlekhene mentshn. m'hot es oyfgegesn.

00:04:34.888 --> 00:04:36.114
antshuldikt mir.

00:04:38.871 --> 00:04:41.447
tsu morgns varft zi mir arayn a tsibele.

00:04:42.786 --> 00:04:47.336
nokh a tog varft zi mir arayn a a knobl. YOU KNOW, GARLIC.

00:04:47.781 --> 00:04:50.880
vos iz dos epes? zi hot mikh oysgeklibn?

00:04:51.190 --> 00:04:53.378
ikh bin geven zeyer interesant tsu visn.

00:04:55.324 --> 00:05:00.425
in der fri flegt men aroysnemt dortn, hot men gedorfn mentshn zey zoln oysreynikn di vash ROOM.

00:05:00.425 --> 00:05:04.599
vayl m'hot undz eyn mol in der fri aroysgelozt in a vash ROOM in der HALL.

00:05:05.567 --> 00:05:11.551
in di HALL hob ikh ir gezen. ikh fleg gebn mentshn zoln UNK, epes a shoyn gevorn a ofitsir.

00:05:12.604 --> 00:05:19.230
SO freg ikh ir, zog ikh, "zog mir, far vos hostu mikh oysgeklibn? ale zenen hungerik!"

00:05:19.962 --> 00:05:24.562
zogt zi tsu mir, vest mikh farshteyn ven ikh vel dir zogn.

00:05:25.075 --> 00:05:29.034
ikh hob a zun, iz er in gantsn enlekh tsu dir,

00:05:29.580 --> 00:05:32.578
un efsher velkhe mame helft im oykhet.

00:05:32.803 --> 00:05:36.189
dos heyst, ayer zun zitst oykhet in tfise ergetsh?

00:05:36.550 --> 00:05:39.041
zogt zi, du zest oys in gantsn azoy vi mayn zun.

00:05:39.418 --> 00:05:45.571
un zi hot, der knobl un tsibl hot mir geSAVED di tsung az di tseyn zoln nisht aroysfaln.

00:05:45.578 --> 00:05:49.723
azoy flegn dokh di tseyn aroysfaln. vayl s'nisht geven keyn VITAMINS.

00:05:51.113 --> 00:06:09.264
ikh bin dortn gezesn biz in nayntstn in nayntstn a- m- se- APRIL.

00:06:09.625 --> 00:06:10.699
velkhe yor?

00:06:10.198 --> 00:06:12.504
NO NO NO NO NO NO NO NO NO.

00:06:12.527 --> 00:06:17.381
in nayntstn NO in v- september.

00:06:17.640 --> 00:06:18.697
in di tfise.

00:06:18.852 --> 00:06:22.072
velkhes yor? vos far a yor iz dos gevezn?

00:06:21.572 --> 00:06:25.987
in finef un fertsikstn. shoyn nokh di milkhome.

00:06:26.044 --> 00:06:29.025
ir hot gehert vi azoy di milkhome hot zikh geendikt?

00:06:29.453 --> 00:06:35.555
m'hot ge- tsu azoy vi m'hot undz gefirt oyf a shpatsir, bin ikh gegangen der letster.

00:06:36.490 --> 00:06:39.032
di zelnerke vos zi hot undz gefirt,

00:06:39.392 --> 00:06:43.807
un ikh hob gezen a fon oyfn o- oyfn bay di tfise.

00:06:44.083 --> 00:06:46.591
freg ikh ir vos far a yontev iz haynt?

00:06:46.665 --> 00:06:49.241
zogt zi, veyst nisht? di milkhome hot zikh geFINISHt.

00:06:49.534 --> 00:06:51.485
azoy hob ikh ir gevust di milkhome hot zikh geFI-

00:06:53.263 --> 00:07:02.791
SO hot men undz genumen fun di tfise aroys, in zibetsetn FEBRUARY.

00:07:05.835 --> 00:07:17.625
un m'hot undz gefirt, ze'mir geforn, a geshikhte fun efsher a vokh, in a lager arayn.

00:07:16.676 --> 00:07:18.823
vu hin? tsu vos a?

00:07:18.323 --> 00:07:21.354
in d- alts tif in Sibir.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:34.334
der nomen funem lager iz gevezn akht un fertsik post kart, post BOX.

00:07:34.334 --> 00:07:36.289
akht un fertsik. dos iz geven.

00:07:37.020 --> 00:07:43.461
dortn bin ikh gevezn efsher tsvey yor. SO ANYWAY, m'hot undz dortn gebrengt.

00:07:44.057 --> 00:07:46.565
m'hot undz gebrengt ze'mir geven in mitn der nakht.

00:07:47.449 --> 00:07:50.801
shneyen biz aher. frest geferlekh.

00:07:51.212 --> 00:07:57.601
m'kumt tsu tsum toyer arayngeyn in tfise in lager arayn, der natshalnik iz nishto, s'ver zol onnemen.

00:07:58.114 --> 00:08:01.500
un di zelner krigstu a komande, leyg zikh.

00:08:01.911 --> 00:08:05.381
oyb s'vet zikh ver oyfshteln vet men dikh shisn on vorenung.

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:09.549
ze'mir azoy gelign efsher tsvey sho.

00:08:10.517 --> 00:08:12.991
biz der natshalnik iz ongekumen, hot undz arayngenumen.

00:08:13.065 --> 00:08:17.649
m'hot undz arayngenumen hot shoyn gemuzt zayn der zeyger efsher arum tsveye draye.

00:08:19.950 --> 00:08:22.863
ken men in ergets nisht aynshlofn, m'darf geyn frier in bod arayn.

00:08:23.933 --> 00:08:28.545
di bod iz geven azoy vayt tsum bayshpil az ikh zol zogn fun danen

00:08:28.545 --> 00:08:38.573
fun danen biz vayter vi Bush-Sheperd. o YEA. a shtik vegs vayter. biz tsum park.

00:08:39.727 --> 00:08:41.611
m'hot undz nokh dem arayngenumen,

00:08:41.702 --> 00:08:45.462
un m'hot ge- un s'geshtanen vu m'darf oyfhengen dos ontuekhts,

00:08:45.462 --> 00:08:49.188
un dos zenen gegangen rern mit elektrik.

00:08:49.954 --> 00:08:54.521
mit tsi gaz, az s'zol oyspareven dos ontuekhts.

00:08:56.265 --> 00:09:01.574
hot got geholfn, keyn v- keyn vareme vaser iz nisht gevezn. dos ershte reye.

00:09:02.205 --> 00:09:04.713
un mit kalte vaser in azelkhene frest?

00:09:04.939 --> 00:09:08.665
dervayl iz aropgefaln a por PANTS oyf di rern,

00:09:08.665 --> 00:09:10.906
un dos gantse ontuekhts iz farbrent gevorn.

00:09:11.689 --> 00:09:14.298
fun mayne PANTS iz geblibn di BELT.

00:09:14.946 --> 00:09:17.522
di resht shoyn nisht. alts iz farbrent gevorn.

00:09:20.312 --> 00:09:25.267
un m'yogt undz nakedikerheyt in dem frost in di barakn arayn krik.

00:09:25.645 --> 00:09:28.500
un mir loyfn nakedikerheyt arayn do ts-

00:09:28.615 --> 00:09:31.528
un ikh hob nokh gehat ikh bin nokh geven mazldik, ikh hob nokh gehat a por shikh.

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:33.885
bin ikh ikh hob nokh gezdonzhet ontsutun di shikh.

00:09:33.885 --> 00:09:35.952
un m'iz gelofn naketerheyt.

00:09:35.952 --> 00:09:39.594
m'iz arayngekumen, m'iz eyner lebn dem andern gezesn, bloyz zikh ontsuvaremen.

00:09:42.908 --> 00:09:45.163
in der fri hot men ongehoybn tsu farshraybn fakhn.

00:09:47.633 --> 00:09:49.719
ANYWAY, dort iz geven a shap.

00:09:50.670 --> 00:09:52.520
un ikh hob zikh farshribn far a shnayder.

00:09:52.948 --> 00:09:55.136
un ikh vil adurkhlozn gevise zakhn.

00:09:55.378 --> 00:09:57.734
m'hot mikh arayngenumen dortn tsu vern a shnayder.

00:09:59.395 --> 00:10:05.751
SO dortn iz gevezn eyner vos er iz gevezn a der hoypt.

00:10:07.191 --> 00:10:09.868
ober er iz gevezn nisht keyn shnayder, er iz geven a galiker.

00:10:11.055 --> 00:10:16.263
hob ikh gezen az er FIT on a uniform an ofitsir vos er bagrobt im.

00:10:18.598 --> 00:10:21.885
zog ikh im shtilerheyt, er iz tsugekumen, ikh bin geshtanen barn tish,

00:10:21.885 --> 00:10:24.178
zog ikh tsu im shtilerheyt, s'vet nisht toygn.

00:10:25.045 --> 00:10:28.509
zogt er, du bist a shnayder? zog ikh a EUROPEAN shnay-

00:10:30.175 --> 00:10:33.260
iz geven der natshalnik, veyst vos a natshalnik iz?

00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:37.678
iz geven der natshalnik fun lager mit yenem, mit an ofitsir.

00:10:38.697 --> 00:10:43.939
zogt er, dem uniform vet makhn er, oyf mir.

00:10:46.155 --> 00:10:51.887
OK. ven? zog ikh, du darfst kumen morgn nokh a mol ontsuFITn.

00:10:52.804 --> 00:10:56.122
un ikh hob genumen UNK, ikh hob gemakht dem uniform.

00:10:56.382 --> 00:11:00.510
ober ikh hob gekrign a por PANTS ontsuton fun front,

00:11:00.786 --> 00:11:06.011
vos a zelner iz geven farvundet un dos blut iz geven farzetst ot azoy o,

00:11:06.793 --> 00:11:10.904
az ikh hob mikh gemiest es ontsuton, ober ikh hob gemuzt, ikh hob nisht gehat vos ontsu-

00:11:11.502 --> 00:11:13.709
un ven ikh hob gemakht dem uniform,

00:11:13.709 --> 00:11:16.828
un der ofitsir hot mikh azoy ongekukt fun oybn biz arop,

00:11:16.969 --> 00:11:19.798
un er iz geven azoy tsufridn fun dem uniform,

00:11:20.715 --> 00:11:27.183
far nakht ruft mikh der na- der OFFICE iz geven in der heykh UPSTAIRS, di shap iz geven der nider.

00:11:27.183 --> 00:11:34.968
ruft mikh aroyf, un er zogt, du, fun haynt mol on vestu zayn der farvalter fun shap.

00:11:35.548 --> 00:11:37.601
UNK.

00:11:38.046 --> 00:11:39.896
zog ikh, NO NO NO NO, ikh vil nisht.

00:11:40.122 --> 00:11:43.626
ikh hob ikh bin shoyn gevezn. ikh hob shoyn genug.

00:11:44.357 --> 00:11:46.916
zogt er, du fargest nisht az bist a geshlosener.

00:11:46.973 --> 00:11:50.724
ikh hob shoyn gehat gekrign, ikh hob shoyn, in in yene tfise, di tsveyte

00:11:50.724 --> 00:11:54.391
ikh bin geven, iz aropgekumen vifl ikh hob gekrign.

00:11:54.432 --> 00:11:59.015
hob ikh gekrign akht yor, di tsveyte, vi ikh hob gezogt vos er hot

00:11:59.072 --> 00:12:02.475
vos er hot er hot zikh nokh dem dertseylt, hot gekrign tsen yor.

00:12:03.207 --> 00:12:09.107
azoy az der dokter hot gekrign akht yor, un der inzhenir hot gekrign finef yor,

00:12:09.214 --> 00:12:14.231
un fun eynem, er iz geven a a inzhenir khemye, a a a shvoger tsum dokter,

00:12:14.231 --> 00:12:17.021
ikh veys nisht vu er iz ahingekumen. I DON'T KNOW UNK.

00:12:17.331 --> 00:12:19.907
ANYWAY, ikh hob gemuzt ibernemen di shap.

00:12:20.402 --> 00:12:25.155
vayter iz geven a ba- a por shabotn iz arayngekumen a tvivilner man,

00:12:25.347 --> 00:12:30.724
un er zogt un nemen im arayn, tu im on fun kop biz di fis in ershte kategorye ontuekhts.

00:12:31.860 --> 00:12:35.567
m'hot mikh m'hot mikh ongeton fun vesh fun ontuekhts fun altsding.

00:12:35.691 --> 00:12:37.879
a bord hob ikh getrogn biz aher,

00:12:38.138 --> 00:12:43.447
er hot mir geshikt in bod arayn, dortn iz shoyn geven, in lager iz geven zikh vu oystsubodn varem.

00:12:43.538 --> 00:12:46.569
un s'geven a BARBER, er hot mir opgeSAHVED, opgeshoyrn, alts.

00:12:47.858 --> 00:12:49.337
ikh hob ibergenumen di shap.

00:12:51.469 --> 00:12:54.230
dortn iz mir nisht nisht shlekht geven.

00:12:54.405 --> 00:12:58.010
esn hob ikh gehat. fun kesl hob ikh nisht gegesn.

00:12:58.945 --> 00:13:05.267
di o azoy vos shteyen mit dir tsuzamen. zi hot gekokht. zi hot gekokht far mir.

00:13:05.863 --> 00:13:08.906
ikh hob gehat ULCERS. nokh far di krig.

00:13:08.906 --> 00:13:15.324
hot zi gezogt az ikh hob gegesn zeyer esn fun kesl, iz geven zoyer. hob ikh alts krikgegibn.

00:13:15.465 --> 00:13:17.568
zogt zi, ikh vel fun dir a mentsh makhn.

00:13:18.351 --> 00:13:21.351
un zi hot ge- gemakht getriknt broyt.

00:13:21.351 --> 00:13:24.471
zi hot gehat a shvester a dokterin oyf der fray,

00:13:24.595 --> 00:13:27.964
flegt zi undz dort shraybn, zi hot arayngeshikt produktn.

00:13:28.290 --> 00:13:30.511
zi hot mikh gehaltn oyfgehaltn dos gantse lebn.

00:13:31.750 --> 00:13:36.485
SO ANYWAY, hob ikh ongefirt mit dos shap.

00:13:37.791 --> 00:13:42.780
ikh hob ikh hob gehat in shap fray.

00:13:43.562 --> 00:13:48.720
keyner hot nisht getort trogn keyn hor, ale zenen geven opgeshoyrn azoy vi shepsn. ikh hob getrogn.

00:13:50.194 --> 00:13:52.494
der natshalnik fun lager flegt zogn,

00:13:52.494 --> 00:13:55.304
dray a zeyger bay tog, m'hot oysgeheytst di banye,

00:13:55.304 --> 00:14:00.864
flegt er araynkumen in shap arayn, Yisak UNK. kum.

00:14:00.864 --> 00:14:04.059
mentshn hobn ongekukt, vos far a frayheyt er hot!

00:14:05.803 --> 00:14:10.825
er hot nisht gekent krign keyn leder oyf keyn mantl, er iz a tsu kleyner, er iz a leytenant.

00:14:10.933 --> 00:14:13.390
ven er volt geven a kapitan volt er gekrign.

00:14:13.785 --> 00:14:19.651
ober tsu mir hot er mir arayngebrengt ale groyse genereler, pulkovnikes, ikh zol zey makhn lederne mantlen.

00:14:19.827 --> 00:14:22.892
hob ikh gezen fun yedn mantl epes aroptsuganvenen.

00:14:23.455 --> 00:14:25.221
un ikh hob im gemakht a mantl.

00:14:26.307 --> 00:14:28.731
azoy az er hot nisht gevust mit mir vos tsu tun.

00:14:29.074 --> 00:14:34.687
biz ven zent ir dortn geblibn in di tfise? biz ven zent ir geblibn in di tfise?

00:14:31.544 --> 00:14:32.368
vos?

00:14:34.187 --> 00:14:37.640
in tfi- in tfise? in lager, dos iz shoyn der lager.

00:14:36.029 --> 00:14:38.112
in lager, yo.

00:14:38.018 --> 00:14:48.647
in lager bin ikh geblibn biz in akht un fertsikstn yor, in in zibetsetn APRIL.

00:14:48.649 --> 00:14:51.815
un ven hot aykh baf- ver hot aykh aroysgeshikt?

00:14:51.822 --> 00:14:54.246
vi azoy hot men aykh aroysgeshikt?

00:14:53.745 --> 00:14:56.911
in zibetsn APRIL hot men mikh aroysgeshikt fun dortn.

00:14:54.852 --> 00:14:58.076
vi azoy? vi azoy? vi azoy?

00:15:01.558 --> 00:15:09.754
zey hobn gevust, der natshalnik fun lager hot gevust, az m'darf mikh bafrayen. s'a geshikhte.

00:15:10.401 --> 00:15:17.752
in di PAPERS mayne, hot geshribn, ven m'hot mikh arestirt, az ikh bin a rusisher birger.

00:15:19.277 --> 00:15:21.363
vayl m'hot dokh aroysgegebn rusishe peser.

00:15:22.416 --> 00:15:25.920
ikh hob nisht gevolt zetsn bin ikh dokh gezetsn zibetsn teg.

00:15:28.356 --> 00:15:31.187
az m'hot gegebn a kuk, m'darf aroys bafrayen,

00:15:31.187 --> 00:15:34.154
in zeks un fertsikstn yor hot men bafrayt ale poylisher.

00:15:34.988 --> 00:15:37.344
zenen aroysgeforn fun fun Rusland.

00:15:37.485 --> 00:15:41.025
az m'hot gekukt di bikher, hot men gezen, lomir zogn mayne,

00:15:41.025 --> 00:15:44.567
hot men gezen, UNK Myanovitsh, bist a rusisher birger.

00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:46.001
UNK.

00:15:47.411 --> 00:15:49.411
vu zent ir geforn fun dort?

00:15:48.705 --> 00:15:51.029
nor vi imer m'hot men mikh bafrayt,

00:15:51.171 --> 00:15:53.713
ikh hob nokh gedorfn zitsn nokh dray yor.

00:15:54.006 --> 00:15:56.109
m'hot mikh bafrayt dray yor befor.

00:15:57.820 --> 00:16:01.222
eyner vos er hot gearbet oyf di geheym- dos iz geven a geheyme arbet,

00:16:01.482 --> 00:16:05.976
iz geven a mol a gemishpeter, hot Stalin aroysgegebn a gezets,

00:16:05.976 --> 00:16:09.998
di ale vos zenen ale vos zenen a mol geven gemishpet torn nisht arbetn oyf keyn geheymer arbet.

00:16:12.180 --> 00:16:14.823
darf men, bafrayt men fun der arbet.

00:16:15.606 --> 00:16:18.840
un ikh hob im getun a sakh toyves, a hitl gemakht, a dos.

00:16:18.897 --> 00:16:21.135
er iz, ikh hob alts gevolt iberkoyfn ale.

00:16:21.934 --> 00:16:24.948
iz er arayngekumen tsu mir eyn mol in shap arayn,

00:16:25.258 --> 00:16:27.446
ven di arbetorers zenen avekgegangen.

00:16:27.722 --> 00:16:32.559
un er zogt tsu mir, mir drot finef un tsvontsik yor, s'iz a geheyme opmakh.

00:16:32.953 --> 00:16:35.765
"ikh vil dir zogn eyn zakh, ikh vil dikh rateven.

00:16:37.442 --> 00:16:43.039
du ze az m'zol dir kenen shikn di PAPERS vos m- m'hot dikh arestirt.

00:16:43.264 --> 00:16:47.387
dortn lign dayne PAPERS, di ale poylishe PAPERS dayne.

00:16:47.387 --> 00:16:50.683
az m'vet zey ibershikn do aher, vet men dikh bafrayen.

00:16:53.305 --> 00:16:54.834
s'hot mir lang genumen.

00:16:55.650 --> 00:16:58.479
ikh bin aroyfgegangen tsu dem natshalnik, vu imer fangt men on?

00:16:58.705 --> 00:17:01.736
ikh vel zogn az ikh vil di PAPERS, vert epes ge- epes UNK.

00:17:02.957 --> 00:17:04.959
bin ikh gekumen, ikh hob im gezogt,

00:17:05.438 --> 00:17:11.119
"s'hot zikh mir gekholemt a kholem, mayn tate iz gekumen in a kholem, az di PAPERS zol men ibershikn do aher."

00:17:11.579 --> 00:17:13.615
zogt er mir, shrayb mir on a bite.

00:17:14.584 --> 00:17:20.383
hob ikh geshribn tsu im, ikh hob geshribn tsu ale groyse natshalnikes. un s'nisht gegangen.

00:17:21.199 --> 00:17:23.403
hob ikh ongeshribn tsvey bites.

00:17:23.967 --> 00:17:27.183
un aroysgeshikt tsu, der lager zol nisht visn.

00:17:27.544 --> 00:17:29.580
ikh hob geshikt a LETTER tsu Stalinen,

00:17:30.025 --> 00:17:33.427
un ikh hob geshikt a LETTER tsum hoypt prokuror fun Rusland.

00:17:34.024 --> 00:17:39.671
ikh hob geshribn az ikh bin a poylisher birger un azoy un azoy un altsding mit gantse mayses gesheftn.

00:17:39.897 --> 00:17:42.270
hot gedoyert efsher dray monatn iz gekumen a entfer.

00:17:42.883 --> 00:17:45.037
ikh gloyb az Stalin hot zey nisht gezen.

00:17:45.803 --> 00:17:51.011
un er shraybt az m'hot adurkhgekukt dayn farbrekhn, muzt opzitsn di gantse akht yor.

00:17:54.409 --> 00:18:03.172
SO ANYWAY, ale mol iz mir gekumen an anderer ofitsir un un gevolt mir zogn a gute psure,

00:18:03.172 --> 00:18:05.540
az s'dreyt zikh epes vegn bafrayen.

00:18:07.234 --> 00:18:10.046
arayngekumen eyn mol a zuntik iz arayngekumen a dokter

00:18:10.288 --> 00:18:15.986
vos iz zi hot di di andere froy hot gehoftn. hot im oysgehoftn a BLOUSE.

00:18:16.093 --> 00:18:20.593
iz er arayngekumen a zuntik, zogt er tsu mir, er hot shoyn gevust UNK.

00:18:20.768 --> 00:18:28.490
zogt er tsu mir, ikh volt dir epes gezogt. nor bist dokh a yid. UNK.

00:18:30.606 --> 00:18:36.000
a yid hot lib oyf a frage fregn a frage. WHICH WHICH IS TRUE.

00:18:36.107 --> 00:18:38.632
oyf a QUESTION, YOU ANSWER A QUESTION.

00:18:39.330 --> 00:18:42.727
SO HE SAID TO ME, I WOULD TELL YOU SOMETHING,

00:18:42.727 --> 00:18:46.293
BUT I I CAN'T BECAUSE YOU WILL ASK EITHER WAY A QUESTION.

00:18:46.823 --> 00:18:50.515
I SAID TO HIM, I'M UNK A DIFFERENT JEW.

00:18:50.515 --> 00:18:56.688
I'M NOT ASKING QUESTIONS. IF YOU WILL TELL ME, I'M, IT'S TRUE?

00:18:57.049 --> 00:19:01.177
HE WAS A DOCTOR. I SAID, YES.

00:19:02.061 --> 00:19:07.640
YOU WILL BE IN SHORTn, IN SHORT TIME, YOU WILL BE FREE.

00:19:07.967 --> 00:19:14.829
I SAID, ha! oyf WHAT oyf oyf vo- oyf vos far a smakh?

00:19:13.410 --> 00:19:14.028
far vos.

00:19:15.055 --> 00:19:18.795
ot, zogt er, I TOLD YOU, THAT YOU WILL ASK YEA A QUESTION.

00:19:19.273 --> 00:19:20.364
ANYWAY,

00:19:21.180 --> 00:19:22.288
m'hot aykh bafrayt.

00:19:23.796 --> 00:19:27.806
UNK A- ANOTHER FEW MONTHS.

00:19:29.483 --> 00:19:37.695
AND THEN CAMP LEANER, natshalnik, ruft mikh arayn un zogt tsu mir azoy.

00:19:38.747 --> 00:19:42.943
"do nisht vayt, hot zikh geefnt a groyse FACTORY,

00:19:43.185 --> 00:19:45.642
mit tsvey hundert ELECTRIC mashinen.

00:19:45.953 --> 00:19:48.292
zey hobn nisht keyn MANAGER nor dikh.

00:19:48.602 --> 00:19:50.655
un ikh muz dikh shikn dortn ahin.

00:19:54.424 --> 00:19:57.321
morgn arbet nisht. ru dikh op.

00:19:57.630 --> 00:20:00.496
s'vet kumen a zelner, er vet dikh nemen, er vet dikh tsufirn tsu der ban,

00:20:00.496 --> 00:20:02.349
un er vet dikh avekfirn dortn ahin."

00:20:05.967 --> 00:20:10.888
m'geyt mir aroysgebn produktn oyfn veg far akht tog.

00:20:13.257 --> 00:20:16.558
shpeter ver ikh gevoyer m'geyt mir gebn far finef teg.

00:20:17.678 --> 00:20:21.097
bay di ende zogt men m'geyt mir gebn bloyz far dray teg.

00:20:22.487 --> 00:20:24.759
m'hot mir epes gegibn dortn oyf a por tog.

00:20:26.672 --> 00:20:29.231
un er hot mir gezogt, der natshalnik,

00:20:29.642 --> 00:20:34.293
"ikh vel dikh tsufirn tsu der ban. oyf mayn oyf mayn kotsh.

00:20:34.975 --> 00:20:37.399
un dortn vet zayn a zelner, er vet dikh ibernemen."

00:20:38.974 --> 00:20:42.512
fayn. tsu morgns zibene in der fri,

00:20:43.024 --> 00:20:46.140
git men a geshrey mayn nomen ikh zol aroysgeyn oyf der vakh.

00:20:47.580 --> 00:20:49.818
ikh nem mayn pekl, ikh gey aroys oyf der vakh,

00:20:49.842 --> 00:20:52.940
finef zelner, mit a hunt,

00:20:53.065 --> 00:20:55.573
un m'heyst ikh zol mir oystun in gantsn naket.

00:20:56.575 --> 00:20:59.033
