00:21:00.642 --> 00:21:05.833
in droysn shteyt a TRUCK, un m'nemt mikh aroyf oyf dem TRUCK,

00:21:06.548 --> 00:21:09.731
un in dem iz ongekumen dem natshalnik's froy.

00:21:10.294 --> 00:21:12.330
un zi makht tsu mir azoy, GOODBYE.

00:21:12.589 --> 00:21:14.692
hob ikh ir oykh geentfert GOODBYE.

00:21:14.715 --> 00:21:16.779
un azoy vi ikh hob ir geentfert GOODBYE,

00:21:16.779 --> 00:21:18.947
hot mir a zelner mit di biks,

00:21:18.947 --> 00:21:22.640
hot er mir ongemostn fun oyvn biz arop az ikh hob gemeynt er hot mikh derharget.

00:21:24.368 --> 00:21:25.881
dos iz geven dos bafrayung.

00:21:25.988 --> 00:21:27.956
m'hot mikh tsugefirt tsu der ban,

00:21:29.380 --> 00:21:34.402
un ikh bin opgezesn a gantser tog biz di ban iz ongekumen fun Vladyevastok.

00:21:35.607 --> 00:21:41.625
un ikh bin geforn o mit di ban biz ikh bin ongekumen

