iz es gevezn may may hot es gemuzt zayn dem tsentn oder dem akhtn un tsen.

00:21:50.571 --> 00:21:52.779
ikh bin ongekumen tsu der poylisher grenets.

00:21:53.967 --> 00:21:59.495
ikh bin ongekumen grade nisht grade punkt tsu der poylisher grenets, ikh bin ongekumen keyn Brisk.

00:21:59.552 --> 00:22:03.140
dortn vu s'gevezn der geto hot men undz arayngenumen.

00:22:03.231 --> 00:22:05.216
dortn ze'mir geven dray teg.

00:22:05.425 --> 00:22:12.078
un m'hot dortn a- a- hot men aroysgenumen oyf a feld aroys nokh di dray teg,

00:22:12.078 --> 00:22:17.214
un m'hot yedn eynem gefregt tsi m'vil blaybn, tsi m'vil blaybn in Rusland.

00:22:17.507 --> 00:22:20.336
ANYWAY, m'hot undz tsugefirt tsu der ban,

00:22:20.663 --> 00:22:23.947
