00:22:40.407 --> 00:22:46.807
un m'hot undz gegebn biletn fray tsu kenen forn nokh Varshe, m'hot gekrign Varshe.

00:22:46.807 --> 00:22:50.182
fun dortn avekforn keyn Varshe.

00:22:50.182 --> 00:22:54.120
Varshe iz shoyn geven a komitet, hob ikh ongehoybn tsu zukhn

00:22:56.235 --> 00:23:02.793
tsu zukhn efsher hot zi zikh farshribn, tsi zi iz aroysgeforn fun Rusland. I DON'T KNOW. nishto.

