00:29:25.575 --> 00:29:28.471
hot er gedorfn epes makhn an ALTERATION.

00:29:28.444 --> 00:29:31.073
ir zent glaykh gekumen keyn Toronto, yo?

00:29:30.537 --> 00:29:31.408
YEA.

00:29:32.899 --> 00:29:36.672
bin ikh hot er gedorfn makhn an ALTERATION, hot er gezogt,

00:29:36.797 --> 00:29:39.845
ikh hob gehert du bist a shnayder, efsher kenstu makhn? zog ikh yo.

00:29:40.003 --> 00:29:42.005
arayngekumen, ikh hob es im gemakht dort.

00:29:42.113 --> 00:29:43.325
shlogt er mir for,
